{
  "stem": "21494.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I went and went, and so many times, you know, I-- I almost was killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, like, somebody-- I didn't have where to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was winter, snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took out the snow, and I pull out the--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the lice, excuse me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here from the--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--from the fur.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I put the fur.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was black, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they was eating alive, me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What can I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I-- I stood by-- there was a small-- [NON-ENGLISH]-- you know, a small [NON-ENGLISH] between a-- Dolhoszyje and-- and [NON-ENGLISH], you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- then I-- I was waiting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were [NON-ENGLISH] the-- the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was waiting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- and-- and I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People were going and coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was waiting until everyone go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was so-- no-- convinced that I need to go there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came there, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He say, wait a moment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Go in the-- in the-- in the shire-- shire.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He say, now nobody's there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think, oye my, God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maybe he wants to kill me, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A-- a big man, you know-- and he called me in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They called me in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I saw maybe six children, or seven children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he gave me right away a-- a glass milk-- warm milk and a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And on the-- on the pitch, you know, where you bake bread wintertime, the children go there to make warm.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I saw one child, like-- like a Jewish child, like another's child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he says, you know why-- why you are this-- new light suffer so much?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, because we didn't believe in Jesus Christ.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
